data.description: Two Brick Flat in Humboldt Park 1/2 block from Chicago Ave. 3 electric meters, Circuit breakers. Cooper water pipes. 2 car garage. Front and rear fences. Area is full of City investments projects as Police and Fire Training Academy, and commercial projects as Amazon, "Humboldt Lit The Terminal". Quick access to Down Town via Pulaski to I-290 or via Chicago Ave and/or Grand Ave. To Be Sold in As-Is Condition.
